title: 132: The Costco Haul Episode (February '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Costco Haul Episode (February '21 Edition)
description: In this week’s episode, Lisa, Mikey & Jamie are trying tasty food finds like Asian spring rolls, seaweed salad, cheesy cheddar crackers, kale chips, an interesting shiitake mushroom snack, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the gang tries an almond cranberry thin cookie that’s an all-around homerun! So go ahead and push play. Then when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the finds in the episode.
itunes:summary: You’ve been waiting for it… It’s our first Costco Haul of the year!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
